OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1784852297
OL,3,CAs Glasgow Commonwealth Games begin,
OL,4,Cwhy do they look so different this
OL,5,Cyear?
OL,7,FThe 2026 Commonwealth Games are set to
OL,8,Fbegin on Thursday evening with an
OL,9,Fopening ceremony held at the Glasgow
OL,10,FHydro.
OL,12,FIt marks the fourth time the games
OL,13,Fhave been held in Scotland, with the
OL,14,Flast being 2014. Birmingham also
OL,15,Fhosted the quad-annual event in 2022.
OL,17,FMore than 70 teams are set to take
OL,18,Fpart but, for a variety of reasons,
OL,19,Fthe 2026 edition will look a little
OL,20,Fdifferent to previous years.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
