CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1784852297
OL,3,CAs Glasgow Commonwealth Games begin,
OL,4,Cwhy do they look so different this
OL,5,Cyear?
OL,7,FSo what should you look out for, and
OL,8,Fwhy have the games had a shakeup this
OL,9,Ftime round?
OL,11,FWhat are the Commonwealth Games?
OL,13,FLike the Olympic Games, the
OL,14,FCommonwealth Games are held every four
OL,15,Fyears.
OL,17,FFrom Friday to August 2, around 3,000
OL,18,Fcompetitors from 74 teams will compete
OL,19,Ffor 215 gold medals across 10
OL,20,Fdifferent disciplines.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1784852297
OL,3,CAs Glasgow Commonwealth Games begin,
OL,4,Cwhy do they look so different this
OL,5,Cyear?
OL,7,FParticipation in the Games is limited
OL,8,Fto member states of the Commonwealth
OL,9,Fof Nations and their territories.
OL,11,FAlthough there are 56 members of the
OL,12,FCommonwealth of Nations, 72 teams
OL,13,Fcurrently participate in the
OL,14,Ftournament as a number of dependent
OL,15,Fterritories compete under their own
OL,16,Fflags.
OL,18,FOnly six teams have attended every
OL,19,FCommonwealth Games: Australia, Canada,
OL,20,FEngland, New Zealand, Scotland and
OL,21,FWales.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1784852297
OL,3,CAs Glasgow Commonwealth Games begin,
OL,4,Cwhy do they look so different this
OL,5,Cyear?
OL,7,FThe 2026 Games are set to include a
OL,8,Frecord number of para-sport events,
OL,9,Fwith 47 opportunities for athletes to
OL,10,Fwin medals.
OL,12,FWhat should you expect from the
OL,13,Fopening ceremony?
OL,15,FThursday evening's opening ceremony is
OL,16,Fset to be held in Glasgow's Hydro
OL,17,Farena.
OL,19,FThis is the first time the opening
OL,20,Fceremony has been held in an indoor
OL,21,Fvenue.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1784852297
OL,3,CAs Glasgow Commonwealth Games begin,
OL,4,Cwhy do they look so different this
OL,5,Cyear?
OL,7,FFor the first time in its history, the
OL,8,Fgames will not be shown on the BBC,
OL,9,Fwith the national broadcaster having
OL,10,Fbeen outbid by TNT Sports.
OL,12,FThe opening ceremony will therefore be
OL,13,Fbroadcast on TNT Sports and HBO Max,
OL,14,Fwith coverage starting at 18:30 BST,
OL,15,Fand uninterrupted viewing from 20:00-
OL,16,F22:00. Channel 5 will also screen the
OL,17,Fopening ceremony live and run a
OL,18,Fnightly highlights show.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1784852297
OL,3,CAs Glasgow Commonwealth Games begin,
OL,4,Cwhy do they look so different this
OL,5,Cyear?
OL,7,FKing Charles, Queen Camilla and new
OL,8,FPrime Minister Andy Burnham will
OL,9,Fattend the event, which will feature
OL,10,Fperformances by KT Tunstall, Callum
OL,11,FBeattie, Nathan Evans, Tom Walker and
OL,12,FSaint Phnx.
OL,14,FWhy are the games being held in
OL,15,FGlasgow?
OL,17,FThe 2026 games was originally meant to
OL,18,Fbe held in the Australian state of
OL,19,FVictoria, however the would-be hosts
OL,20,Fwithdrew in July 2023 over concerns
OL,21,Faround increasing costs.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1784852297
OL,3,CAs Glasgow Commonwealth Games begin,
OL,4,Cwhy do they look so different this
OL,5,Cyear?
OL,7,FVictoria had agreed to host the event
OL,8,Fa year earlier, after the Commonwealth
OL,9,FGames Federation (CGF) struggled to
OL,10,Ffind a host.
OL,12,FThe cost was originally estimated to
OL,13,Fbe A$2.6bn (#1.35 billion), but the
OL,14,Fprojected bill soared to more than A$6
OL,15,Fbillion (#3.11 billion).
OL,17,FAfter discussions with numerous
OL,18,Fdifferent cities, Glasgow was
OL,19,Fconfirmed as the replacement host city
OL,20,Fin September 2024, albeit with a
OL,21,Fscaled-back version to keep costs down.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
