OL,3,CAs Glasgow Commonwealth Games begin,
OL,4,Cwhy do they look so different this
OL,5,Cyear?
OL,7,FWhich sports are included?
OL,9,FThis years event will feature less
OL,10,Fthan half the number of sports than
OL,11,FBirmingham's 2024 games.
OL,13,FDiving, badminton, beach volleyball,
OL,14,Fcricket, hockey, rugby sevens, squash,
OL,15,Ftable tennis, triathlon, and wrestling
OL,16,Fhave all been dropped from the 2022
OL,17,Fprogramme.
OL,19,FThese ten that will included in this
OL,20,Fyear's games are:
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
