OL,3,CAs Glasgow Commonwealth Games begin,
OL,4,Cwhy do they look so different this
OL,5,Cyear?
OL,7,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,8,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,9,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,10,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,12,FWhat else has changed?
OL,14,FThe overall size of the 2026 event
OL,15,Fwill be noticeably smaller.
OL,17,FThe Scotstoun Stadium, which will be
OL,18,Fhome to several athletic events, will
OL,19,Fhost just 11,000 spectators, down from
OL,20,Fthe 50,000 cheering on competitors in
OL,21,Fthe 2014 Games.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31810
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1784852297
OL,3,CAs Glasgow Commonwealth Games begin,
OL,4,Cwhy do they look so different this
OL,5,Cyear?
OL,7,FThe money being spent on these games
OL,8,Fis also down. In 2014 the budget came
OL,9,Fto #543 million, but the 2026 Games
OL,10,Fare set to cost just #150 million,
OL,11,Fwith no public money being spent on
OL,12,Fthe event at all.
OL,14,FThe Commonwealth Games Foundation
OL,15,F(CGF) is investing #100m of this, with
OL,16,Fthe remainder coming from ticketing,
OL,17,Fsponsorship, broadcast rights and
OL,18,Fmerchandise.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
