OL,3,CAs Glasgow Commonwealth Games begin,
OL,4,Cwhy do they look so different this
OL,5,Cyear?
OL,7,FOne event to look out for will be the
OL,8,FCommonwealth mile, which is making its
OL,9,Ffirst appearance in the event's
OL,10,Fschedule in 60 years. It replaces the
OL,11,F1,500 metres event, and is the only
OL,12,Fnonmetric event with official
OL,13,Frecognition for world records and
OL,14,Frankings.
OL,16,FScotland's Josh Kerr, the new world
OL,17,Frecord-holder, will be favourite for
OL,18,Fthe men's event, with women competing
OL,19,Fin the discipline for the first time.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
