OL,3,CAs Glasgow Commonwealth Games begin,
OL,4,Cwhy do they look so different this
OL,5,Cyear?
OL,7,FThe more than 3,000 athletes taking
OL,8,Fpart in the 2026 Games will have to
OL,9,Ffork out for their own accommodation
OL,10,Fas well, with organisers deciding not
OL,11,Fto build an official athlete village.
OL,13,FWhen can I see each sport?
OL,15,F0930 - 1625 Bowls and Para Bowls
OL,17,F1000 - 2130 3x3 Basketball & 3x3
OL,18,FWheelchair Basketball
OL,20,F1000 - 2115 Artistic Gymnastics
OL,21,F(medals)
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
